* goals / design
	: a guile program that implements a dsl for defining csound synthesizers
	[_] low level bindings
		[X] low level rendering of opcodes and instruments with named parameters
		[X] low level rendering of notes with named parameters
		[X] low level rendering of csd files
			: unit test now verifies csound creates audio from the csd
	[_] high level bindings
		[_] expressions to generate variants of instruments
		[_] expressions to elaborate sequences of notes
		[_] linking instruments via channels, zak, or ftables for modulation
		[_] expression that generates instrument plus others for modulation
			: the main instrument uses channels, ftables, or zak space to
			: read parameters at runtime, modified by other instruments
